OL,3,CAround 50 firefighters continue to
OL,4,Ctackle wildfire in Hilltown
OL,6,FAround 50 firefighters are continuing
OL,7,Fto tackle a wildfire in Hilltown.
OL,9,FThe Northern Ireland Fire and Rescue
OL,10,FService (NIFRS) said they are battling
OL,11,Fa fire front of over 500m at the
OL,12,FSandbank Road.
OL,14,FCrews are expected to work throughout
OL,15,FTuesday and the public have been asked
OL,16,Fto avoid the area.
OL,18,FElsewhere, a wildfire in the Ballagh
OL,19,FRoad area of the Mourne Mountains has
OL,20,Fnow been dealt with.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
