OL,3,CAround 50 firefighters continue to
OL,4,Ctackle wildfire in Hilltown
OL,6,FMore than 80 firefighters tackled the
OL,7,Fwildfire at its height after they were
OL,8,Fcalled at 6.44pm on Saturday.
OL,10,FThe blaze which spanned 1000 hectares
OL,11,Fis believed to have been started
OL,12,Fdeliberately.
OL,14,FThe incident was dealt with by 10.08am
OL,15,Fon Tuesday.
OL,17,FThe NIFRS has warned the public to
OL,18,Fstay vigilant to fire in the
OL,19,Fcountryside and have asked them to
OL,20,Fadhere to their fire safety advice.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/3
